01:13.173 --> 01:15.507
Oh, gosh!
Oh, mike!

01:15.509 --> 01:17.575
Adult mark:<i> I never</i>
<i> missed an award show.</i>

01:17.611 --> 01:20.778
<i> The oscars, the tonys,</i>
<i> the marks...</i>

01:20.815 --> 01:23.114
