the name of the "beef bandit."

02:54.608 --> 02:59.677
Mike critch
for the award-winning vocm news.

02:59.713 --> 03:01.880
Mm, stunning!

03:02.015 --> 03:03.682
Yes!

03:03.751 --> 03:05.884
